#, python-format
msgid ""
"I'm %(name)s, your SUMO Community Manager. On behalf of the Customer Experience team, I'd love to thank you for registering as a contributor at SUMO a.k.a. <a "
"href=\"%(home_url)s\">SUpport.MOzilla.org</a>. We're so excited you've joined us! Mozilla wouldn't be what it is today without the passionate contributions from people like you."
